'''谢尔顿·H·哈里斯'''（{{lang|en|'''Sheldon H. Harris'''}}，{{bd|1928年|8月|2002年|8月31日|catIdx=Harris, Sheldon H.}}），出生于[[美国|美国]][[纽约|纽约]]，在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]逝世。他曾获得[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]博士学位，[[加州州立大學北嶺分校|加州州立大學北嶺分校]]名誉教授。他长期从事美国现代史研究，细菌战研究专家。<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/04/us/sheldon-harris-74-historian-of-japan-s-biological-warfare.html |title= Sheldon Harris, 74, Historian Of Japan's Biological Warfare |author= Lewis, Paul |date= September 4, 2002 |work= [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate= July 5, 2012 |archive-date= 2018-06-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180625110653/https://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/04/us/sheldon-harris-74-historian-of-japan-s-biological-warfare.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://articles.latimes.com/2002/sep/06/local/me-harris6 |title= Sheldon H. Harris, 74; Historian Detailed Japan's Germ Warfare |author= Trounson, Rebecca |date= September 6, 2002 |work= [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate= July 5, 2012 |archive-date= 2015-10-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151024064644/http://articles.latimes.com/2002/sep/06/local/me-harris6 |dead-url= no }}</ref>著有《[[死亡工厂|死亡工厂]]——美国掩盖的日本细菌战犯罪》（{{lang|en|Factories of Death: Japanese Biological Warfare 1932-45 and The American Cover-up}}, ISBN 0415932149），1994出版。中文版由[[王选_(女)|王选]]翻译，[[上海人民出版社|上海人民出版社]]出版。

